snippet.title: The Eminence in Shadow: Master of Garden RPG Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-register for massive rewards at https://got.cr/eis_announce_yt

Not the main character, not the last boss. The one who lurks in the shadows. 

The latest anime RPG coming to iOS, Android, and soon after to PC based on the new hit anime, "The Eminence in Shadow," is now available for pre-registration!
